						<div class="postbody">I had worked out a system that was very similar to this for the GBA, but the two shoulder buttons do make a huge difference.<br /><br />Using all 8 cardinal directions plus each of A,B, AB, neither, gets you 32 different combinations. Start could let you switch to a different plane for rare things.</div>

